description: Under normal circumstances, the fund will invest at least 80% of its total assets in component securities of the index. The index tracks the performance of (i) long position in the most recently issued 30-year Treasury Inflation-Protected Securities ("TIPS") and (ii) duration-adjusted short position in U.S. Treasury bonds of, in aggregate, approximate equivalent duration dollars to the TIPS. The fund is non-diversified.
name: ProShares - Inflation Expectations ETF
